OL,5,Cemergency
OL,7,F#438 million needs to be spent every
OL,8,Fsingle year to halt the nature
OL,9,Femergency in Wales.
OL,11,FA report, shared exclusively with ITV
OL,12,FCymru Wales, shows a substantial
OL,13,Fincrease in the amount of funding
OL,14,Fneeded as nature and species struggles
OL,15,Fto survive in our constantly evolving
OL,16,Fclimate.
OL,18,FOne in six species are now seen as at
OL,19,Fthreat of extinction in Wales and
OL,20,Fsince 1994, there has been a 20%
OL,21,Fdecrease in wildlife in the country.
