OL,7,FLast year - it was just #158 million.
OL,8,FThis year it's nearly three times
OL,9,Fhigher.
OL,11,FThis is partly due to inflations and
OL,12,Fnew estimates but also as a result of
OL,13,Fthe worsening picture. The report, by
OL,14,FWales Environment Link, has revealed
OL,15,Ften key areas that need action to help
OL,16,Frecover nature.
OL,18,FThe suggested actions include:
