OL,7,FKaren Whitfield, Joint Director of
OL,8,FWales Environment Link, said: "The key
OL,9,Fproblems for nature loss at the moment
OL,10,Fare things like loss of habitat,
OL,11,Fpollution and the impact of climate
OL,12,Fchange.
OL,14,F"The report looks at existing
OL,15,Fgovernment spending and also
OL,16,Fidentifies areas where we feel that
OL,17,Fthere is a gap in funding compared to
OL,18,Fwhat we would need to see these
OL,19,Factions progress properly.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/10
