OL,5,Cemergency
OL,7,F"We really feel that investment (in
OL,8,Fnature) needs to be prioritised
OL,9,Fbecause we're not seeing the scale and
OL,10,Fpace of change that we need in terms
OL,11,Fof restoring nature."
OL,13,FThe State of Nature report in 2023
OL,14,Fconcluded that Wales is one of the
OL,15,Fmost nature depleted countries in the
OL,16,Fworld with dwindling species,
OL,17,Fincluding the Atlantic salmon and
OL,18,Fcurlew.
