OL,7,FMs Whitfield said that this decline is
OL,8,Fdue to "loss of habitat, pollution,
OL,9,Finvasive species, unsustainable
OL,10,Fharvesting of fish for example in our
OL,11,Foceans and climate change."
OL,13,FShe continued: "There are multiple
OL,14,Fcauses for this and that's why there
OL,15,Fare multiple things that we need to
OL,16,Faddress and that's why prioritisation
OL,17,Fof this extra spend is so important
OL,18,Fright now."
