OL,7,FMr Irranca-Davies said he "welcomes
OL,8,Fthe report", explaining that "there's
OL,9,Fnever going to be enough taxpayer
OL,10,Fmoney to deal with the quantum of
OL,11,Ffunds we need going into environmental
OL,12,Frestoration and the wider
OL,13,Fenvironmental eco services.
OL,15,F"So we do need to think creatively and
OL,16,Fthe engagement that we're having
OL,17,Fcurrently with environmental
OL,18,Forganisations but also those who would
OL,19,Fbe interested in community
OL,20,Finterventions within this area."
