OL,7,FHe added: "I recognise what they've
OL,8,Fidentified which is that we're never
OL,9,Fgoing to fill that gap simply through
OL,10,Ftaxpayer funding, simply through Welsh
OL,11,FGovernment, local authority funding
OL,12,Fwith the best will in the world.
OL,14,F"What we need to do is be very
OL,15,Fcreative together and try and fill
OL,16,Fthat gap in funding because we need to
OL,17,Fdo it if we're going to deal with the
OL,18,Fnature emergency, but also the climate
